description: Development of a secure payroll automation platform to streamline salary processing, deductions, and compliance with local tax laws.
Creation of a self-service web portal for employees to access payslips, request leave, and update personal information.
Building a mobile app for Android/iOS to allow employees and managers to request, approve, and track leaves on the go.
Design and deployment of an applicant tracking system to streamline recruitment workflows, job postings, and candidate evaluations.
Creation of a central HR data warehouse to consolidate employee, payroll, and recruitment data for reporting and analytics.
Automating the employee onboarding process including document submission, IT setup, and first-week training schedule.
Development of a corporate LMS to manage employee e-learning courses, certifications, and compliance training.
A gamified recognition system where employees can award points and badges for teamwork, innovation, and leadership.
An HR analytics tool to track leadership readiness, identify key talent, and plan succession for critical roles.
